Nor friend's nor parent's love
Could reach this deep or wide;
Sinners redeemed must sing
A Savior's love applied.
Behold, God's Son on Golgotha;
For you and me He's crucified.

Sinners redeemed defeat
The snake that came and lied;
Nothing can keep us now
From Christ's own loving side.
Behold, God's Son on Golgotha;
For you and me He's crucified.
